title: Mariah Carey arrives in Dubai, spotted at Burj Khalifa
text:
Mariah Carey arrives in Dubai, spotted at Burj Khalifa By   Pic: Supplied 
Global superstar Mariah Carey has landed in Dubai ahead of her Emirates Airline Dubai Jazz Festival concert this Thursday, February 23 at Dubai Media City Amphitheatre. 
The award-winning artist decided to immerse herself in a cultural excursion starting with a visit at the world's tallest building, Burj Khalifa this afternoon. 
Mariah Carey arrived in a red Bentley and posed in front of the Burj Khalifa with boyfriend Bryan Tanaka. She is wearing Tom Ford jacket, Alia Shoes and Belt, and Gucci New Collection jeans.
